## Session Log ‚Äî Apr 26, 2026 (Agent-written, ~06:00‚Äì12:00 EDT)

### Key Events & Fixes

**Gateway auth failures at startup (~06:06)**
- Symptom: `No credentials found for profile "anthropic:claude-cli"` ‚Äî 4 consecutive failures before session initialized
- Fix: Gateway restarted cleanly; session came up on next cycle
- Lesson: `claude-cli` OAuth profile causes 30s timeout each heartbeat cycle ‚Äî removed later in session

**OPENAI_API_KEY / LanceDB troubleshooting (~06:08‚Äì06:21)**
- Attempted to enable memory-lancedb with OpenAI key ‚Üí 429 quota exceeded
- Attempted Ollama embedding switch ‚Üí lancedb hardcoded to OpenAI only (not configurable)
- Decision: rolled back lancedb to disabled; stayed on memory-core
- Fix applied later: switched `agents.defaults.memorySearch` to `provider: ollama`, `model: nomic-embed-text`

**Memory search properly fixed (~09:00)**
- `agents.defaults.memorySearch.provider = "ollama"` + `model = "nomic-embed-text"` via config
- 154 files / 904 chunks indexed; memory search now free, local, no API dependency

**Cron model prefix deprecated (#2)**
- All `claude-cli/claude-haiku-4-5` references in cron jobs ‚Üí `anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5`

**`anthropic:claude-cli` auth profile removed (#4)**
- Removed OAuth profile; gateway now uses API key directly
- Eliminates 30s timeout delay on every heartbeat cycle

**Heartbeat re-enabled (#5)**
- Was disabled since April 19 (was burning full session context)
- Re-enabled at 30m interval with `isolatedSession: true`, `lightContext: true`
- First run: 18k tokens, 98% cached ‚Äî very cheap

**Apple Calendar CLI set as default**
- `apple-calendar-cli` confirmed installed, calendar access granted, iCloud calendars visible
- Documented in TOOLS.md and MEMORY.md as primary calendar tool
- Google Calendar tools demoted to secondary/fallback only

**Git author config fixed**
- Problem: global git config was using `reillyrd58@gmail.com` ‚Äî breaks Vercel builds for reillydesignstudio
- Fix: Global ‚Üí `robert.reilly@peraton.com` (Vercel requirement); workspace local ‚Üí `reillyrd58@gmail.com`
- 3 stale worktrees pruned
- Bob noted: always say "pushed to `momo-kibigango` main" or "pushed to `reillydesignstudio` main" ‚Äî never just "pushed to main"

**Archive sweep safety script**
- Created `scripts/safe-archive.sh` ‚Äî greps cron, scripts, workspace files, LaunchAgents before archiving
- Prevents repeat of generate-status.sh incident (lesson learned April 26)

**Submodule cleanup**
- `lucianandgideon` ‚Äî 196 asset files were deleted; restored
- `reillydesignstudio` repo ‚Äî 6 portfolio images + signature-logo.png deleted; restored
- `reillyrd58-ai` org push access missing ‚Üí saved to Things 3 for later

**Rocket.Chat community plugin installed**
- `alexwoo-awso/openclaw-rocketchat` installed (more maintained than bundled plugin)
- Not yet configured (needs RC server URL + creds) ‚Üí saved to Things 3

**`adaptive` thinking ‚Üí `medium`**
- Silences log warning; Sonnet 4-6 doesn't support `adaptive`

**Memory index rebuild**
- All 154 files re-indexed after Ollama provider switch

**OpenClaw version confirmed**
- Already on latest stable 2026.4.24; beta has ENOTEMPTY fix but staying on stable

### Decisions Made
- Apple Calendar CLI is now the primary/default calendar tool for all operations
- Memory search: Ollama/nomic-embed-text (local, free, permanent)
- Git global author: `robert.reilly@peraton.com` (Vercel); workspace local: `reillyrd58@gmail.com`
- Rocket.Chat config deferred (Things 3)
- `reillyrd58-ai` org access deferred (Things 3)
- Mac Studio M1 Max 32GB is the recommended second machine for local LLM inference ($900‚Äì$1,100 on eBay)

### Open Priority Items (as of ~12:00 EDT)
**P1 ‚Äî Security**
1. Slack `groupPolicy=open` ‚Üí set to allowlist (CRITICAL)
2. Phantom `plugins.allow` entries ‚Üí remove `anthropic`, `brave`, `memory-core`, `memory-lancedb`

**P2 ‚Äî Capabilities**
3. Active Memory plugin (auto-injects memory context pre-reply)
4. Tailscale integration (remote access from iPhone)
5. iMessage channel enable
6. reillyrd58 Gmail OAuth re-auth (browser step needed)
7. Rocket.Chat full config (deferred)

**P3 ‚Äî Improvements**
8. Total Recall Observer ‚Üí upgrade from Haiku to Sonnet
9. Talk Voice / MLX Speech (local, experimental)
10. memory-wiki plugin
11. Webhooks plugin
12. OpenRouter credits top-up

### Commits Today (momo-kibigango main)
- `fbb105f` fix: restore generate-status.sh (pre-session)
- `90ccc21` feat: Apple Calendar CLI set as default calendar tool
- `b03f94b` chore: fix git author config, prune stale worktrees, add safe-archive.sh

### Auto-summary [14:58] (fallback ‚Äî no transcript)
**Commits:**
- f85d2be chore: session state ‚Äî active memory events, cli images, dreams short-term recall
- 88876d5 docs: update email auth status ‚Äî rdreilly2010 active, reillyrd58 expired
